00:00:35.050 --> 00:00:38.739
You must see your dentist first before you
start whitening, because if you have a lot

00:00:38.739 --> 00:00:43.790
of dental work, such as veneers, crowns, bridges,
this porcelain will not change color with

00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:45.640
the bleach, and your real teeth will.

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:49.130
So if you get a great result from bleaching,
then your teeth will be different colors,

00:00:49.130 --> 00:00:50.130
and doesn't look great.

00:00:50.130 --> 00:00:51.130
Oh, multi-colored mouth.

00:00:51.130 --> 00:00:52.130
That’s not good.

00:00:52.130 --> 00:00:53.309
So it defeats the purpose of bleaching.

00:00:53.309 --> 00:00:56.940
And if you have a lot of cavities or broken
down teeth, you're also not a candidate for

00:00:56.940 --> 00:00:57.940
