00:00:57.940 --> 00:01:00.300
Because if you have decay, the bleach will
get into the tooth and will cause extreme

00:01:00.300 --> 00:01:01.300
sensitivity.

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:03.250
So you should see your dentist before you
start bleaching.

