there silica particles.

00:03:49.710 --> 00:03:54.400
So, what that does is acts as a minor abrasive
to actually remove the surface stains and

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:55.819
make your teeth appear whiter.

00:03:55.819 --> 00:03:56.819
And they're great.

00:03:56.819 --> 00:04:00.850
And there's no harm to using them, as long
as you use a soft toothbrush, you are not

00:04:00.850 --> 00:04:02.080
