White, this is going to actually remove surface

00:04:10.590 --> 00:04:11.590
stains.

00:04:11.590 --> 00:04:14.040
But it’s not going to bleach your teeth,
it’s going to remove surface stains to make

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:15.040
your teeth appear whiter.

